    <!--
      Page margins and a name/date header are set in the publication file, inside
      <publication><common><worksheet ...>, not on the worksheets themselves.
      Each activity is a subsection whose title is the activity name. To activate
      one, uncomment its xi:include and delete the placeholder paragraph. The
      href is relative to THIS file.
    -->
  </introduction>

